@DATABASE "Kendo Warrior"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - K - Kendo Warrior"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                               Kendo Warrior
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38342,0)"}         38342,0 
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38225,183)"}         38225,183
@{"1 Hit Kills    " rxs "address command zxampoke(38986,0)"}         38986,0
@{"Lives = x      " rxs "address command zxampoke(37126,255)"}         37126,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).



                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
